                <p class="text-justify">Wood mulch is a popular landscaping material known for its benefits, but its production raises environmental concerns...</p>

                <h3 class="text-primary">Health Risks</h3>
                <p class="text-justify">Exposure to wood dust has been linked to respiratory conditions such as asthma, bronchitis, and COPD...</p>

                <h3 class="text-primary">Environmental Impact</h3>
                <p class="text-justify">Wood dust pollution affects local ecosystems and contributes to overall air pollution...</p>

                <h3 class="text-primary">Mitigation Strategies</h3>
                <p class="text-justify">Using advanced dust collection systems and implementing regulations can help reduce emissions...</p>

